{
  "name": "Sleep of the Deep",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Genjutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p></p><p>Your chakra creeps into the dreams of others, haunting and terrifying them. Choose any number of sleeping creatures that you are aware of within range. Creatures that do not need to sleep, cannot be targeted.</p><p>The creatures must make a Wisdom Saving Throw. On a failed save they do not benefits from any form of rest for the duration and when they awaken from any rest they may take, they gains 2 ranks of Exhaustion and are Demoralized for as long as they have any ranks of Exhaustion inflicted by this jutsu.</p>",
